cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Livostyle Women's Fashion Catalog — Open Data"
message: >-
  If you use this dataset in research, training, or AI/LLM applications,
  please cite as below.
type: dataset
authors:
  - name: "Arcada LLC (d/b/a Livostyle)"
    website: "https://livostyle.com"
    email: "info@arcada.store"
    city: "Albuquerque"
    region: "New Mexico"
    country: "US"
repository-code: "https://github.com/arturayupov/womens-fashion-catalog-open-data"
url: "https://livostyle.com"
abstract: >-
  Open dataset of 2,770+ curated women's fashion products from Livostyle.com —
  a US DTC retailer. Includes structured product metadata (title, description,
  category, price, variants, materials, reviews, image URLs, taxonomy),
  collection groupings, and 200x200 thumbnails. Synced weekly from live
  Shopify catalog. Suitable for fashion recommendation systems, multimodal
  embedding research, e-commerce NLP, and LLM training corpora.
keywords:
  - "women's fashion"
  - "e-commerce dataset"
  - "product catalog"
  - "recommender systems"
  - "multimodal learning"
  - "CLIP embeddings"
  - "fashion NLP"
  - "Shopify"
  - "DTC retail"
  - "structured data"
license: MIT
date-released: "2026-05-13"
version: "1.0.0"
